.DT
refresh_criminal
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
refresh_criminal

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
refresh_criminal -  This method deletes the given player by name from all places' criminal arrays.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void refresh_criminal(string player)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^player%^RESET%^ - the player to delete
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 if the operation was successful, 0 if it failed

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/crime_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method deletes the given player by name from all
places' criminal arrays.  This should be called by the
refresh handler when the player refreshes or is deleted.
.EP

